dict.string: The next morning, Thomas found himself on an unfamiliar island. It was quiet and very misty. As Thomas explored, he heard strange sounds. Rusty wheels rattled on old rails, and wild whistles echoed all around him. Then, as Thomas rounded a bend, he made an amazing discovery. . . .
